of Laramie's apology to me.

253
00:17:16,703 --> 00:17:20,541
I like reading the tabloids.
I think they're fun.

254
00:17:20,666 --> 00:17:23,335
- I think you're drunk.
- I think you're cute.

255
00:17:23,460 --> 00:17:26,505
Your pictures
hurt people.

256
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:28,841
Do they?
The irony...

257
00:17:28,966 --> 00:17:31,468
