but nobody wants to date the butcher.

259
00:17:36,348 --> 00:17:41,937
My job is to provide
a window of reality for society.

260
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:45,148
It's up to them whether they want
to look through it or not.

261
00:17:45,232 --> 00:17:48,026
Come on.
Have you ever bought a tabloid?

262
00:17:48,151 --> 00:17:52,155
- Guilty as charged.
- Don't feel guilty. Guilty's bad.

263
00:17:52,239 --> 00:17:54,157
I mean, everyone wants
to have a...

264
00:17:54,241 --> 00:17:57,619
little peek, huh?

265
00:17:57,703 --> 00:18:00,581
See?
It's human nature.

266
00:18:01,999 --> 00:18:04,710
Look, there's a...
there's a premiere tonight...

267
00:18:04,793 --> 00:18:07,337
and an after party
I'm covering.

268
00:18:07,421 --> 00:18:08,422
Come with me, as my guest...

269
00:18:08,422 --> 00:18:09,840
Come with me, as my guest...

270
00:18:09,923 --> 00:18:13,177
and, um, see things
from an entirely different perspective...

271
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:15,179
mine.

272
00:18:15,262 --> 00:18:17,639
Hey, do a shot with me
and then tell me your story.

273
00:18:17,723 --> 00:18:19,766
I'm a good listener.

274
00:18:19,892 --> 00:18:22,186
- Really?
- Uh-huh.

275
00:18:22,269 --> 00:18:24,271
Listen to this...
No.

276
00:18:27,316 --> 00:18:29,651
What do you say, Marcy?
You want to have a little adventure?

277
00:18:35,908 --> 00:18:38,869
- It's beautiful. You should come and see it.
- Yeah?

278
00:18:38,952 --> 00:18:41,455
So, when...
Saturday, can you come? Or...

279
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:44,208
- Saturday would be great.
- Hey, Bo. How's it going, mate?

280
00:18:44,291 --> 00:18:46,668
- Good to see you again. Remember me?
