what's bothering you, honey?

291
00:19:28,919 --> 00:19:31,630
I just think it's interesting,
that's all.

292
00:19:31,713 --> 00:19:34,633
- You were in London last spring.
- Right.

293
00:19:34,758 --> 00:19:36,718
