get jealous...

294
00:19:36,802 --> 00:19:40,138
if somebody winks at their husband
at the company Christmas party.

295
00:19:40,264 --> 00:19:44,476
Half the civilized world
wants my husband.

296
00:19:44,601 --> 00:19:46,562
How do you think
that makes me feel?

297
00:19:46,645 --> 00:19:49,189
You know what that guy said tonight
is bullshit, right?

298
00:19:49,314 --> 00:19:52,693
- Yeah, I know.
- Okay.

299
00:19:52,818 --> 00:19:55,362
I guess it's all just new to me, you know?

300
00:19:55,487 --> 00:19:57,823
It's new to me too, honey.
And I'm...

301
00:19:57,948 --> 00:19:59,867
You know, every day I'm learning.

302
00:20:03,829 --> 00:20:05,914
Abby!

303
00:20:05,998 --> 00:20:09,376
- Bo! Look at me! Look at me! Look at me!

304
00:20:09,501 --> 00:20:11,920
- Look at me!
- Hey, Bo! Big shot!

305
00:20:12,004 --> 00:20:14,006
- Look at me!
- I can't see a thing.

306
00:20:14,131 --> 00:20:15,716
Bo! Bo!

307
00:20:15,841 --> 00:20:17,801
Bo, slow down!

308
00:20:19,678 --> 00:20:21,471
- Daddy!
- It's all right, son. It's okay.

309
00:20:21,555 --> 00:20:23,724
Son of a bitch!

310
00:20:23,849 --> 00:20:25,767
Takin' the front!

311
00:20:25,851 --> 00:20:27,895
Okay, Leonard. Box him in.

312
00:20:36,653 --> 00:20:39,573
- Hold on!

313
00:21:31,250 --> 00:21:34,044
- Len! Come on. Let's go.

314
00:21:34,127 --> 00:21:35,921
Come on. Come on.

315
00:21:43,095 --> 00:21:45,514
Hello, sweetie.

316
00:21:45,597 --> 00:21:48,934
Yeah, there's been a terrible accident
on, uh, 5th and Flower.

317
00:21:49,059 --> 00:21:50,936
We need an ambulance.

318
00:22:02,281 --> 00:22:04,408
Oh, yeah.

319
00:22:21,466 --> 00:22:23,969
Hey, Marcy.
Hey, honey.

320
00:22:24,094 --> 00:22:26,722
Everything's gonna be fine, okay?
Come on.

321
00:22:26,805 --> 00:22:29,391
Everything's fine. There's an ambulance
on the way already.

322
00:22:29,474 --> 00:22:32,269
They're not hurt that bad.
We'll go back on my boat and have a drink.

323
00:22:32,352 --> 00:22:34,104
- Okay? I'll be right back.
- All right.

324
00:22:34,188 --> 00:22:36,190
- Okay? Okay?
- Okay.

325
00:22:40,694 --> 00:22:43,739
Let's go. Clear out. We're finished here.

326
00:22:43,822 --> 00:22:45,824
Go! Go! Go! Come on!

327
00:22:45,949 --> 00:22:47,826
Go!

328
00:23:33,080 --> 00:23:34,998
Hi.

329
00:23:36,124 --> 00:23:38,710
How is she?

330
00:23:38,836 --> 00:23:41,630
She's in recovery.
I had to remove her spleen.

331
00:23:46,051 --> 00:23:50,180
The next few weeks will be very difficult, Bo.
She'll be in a lot of pain.

332
00:23:50,264 --> 00:23:54,268
We'll manage that with medication,
watch her very carefully.

333
00:23:55,853 --> 00:23:58,730
Now, let's talk about
your little guy here.

334
00:23:58,856 --> 00:24:01,733
He's stable.
His vitals are good.

335
00:24:01,817 --> 00:24:05,112
But comas are
a tricky thing, Bo.

336
00:24:05,237 --> 00:24:07,781
All we can do is wait.

337
00:24:07,906 --> 00:24:09,783
Okay.

338
00:24:12,161 --> 00:24:15,914
- Can we be left alone?
- Absolutely.

339
00:24:16,039 --> 00:24:18,500
Thank you, Doctor.

340
00:25:11,678 --> 00:25:14,014
Daddy!

341
00:25:28,612 --> 00:25:31,198
- You taped me?
- Mm-hmm.

342
00:25:31,323 --> 00:25:33,408
The wine... You mu...
You must have put something in it...

343
00:25:33,492 --> 00:25:35,410
Obviously it made you
quite amorous.

344
00:25:35,494 --> 00:25:38,914
It's a shame, Marcy,
you don't remember it.

345
00:25:38,997 --> 00:25:42,960
Still going to the police to tell them who
caused Laramie's accident? Think again!

346
00:25:43,043 --> 00:25:46,296
Not only will I attach that
to every porno site on the Internet...

347
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:50,425
