and see you every day, okay?

354
00:26:29,381 --> 00:26:32,217
It's okay, honey.
He can hear you, sweetie. All right?

355
00:26:32,342 --> 00:26:34,303
Okay.

356
00:26:37,222 --> 00:26:39,224
One second, honey.

357
00:26:39,308 --> 00:26:42,060
I'm gonna go out and talk to
the detective. I'll be right back.

358
00:26:42,186 --> 00:26:44,813
Honey, wake up and you can
have whatever you want.

359
00:26:46,565 --> 00:26:48,650
- Hi, Bo.
- How are you, Detective?

360
00:26:48,734 --> 00:26:53,280
