614
00:49:11,451 --> 00:49:13,203
Shh! I'll be fine.

615
00:49:13,287 --> 00:49:15,664
- Okay. All right.

616
00:49:15,747 --> 00:49:17,833
I'll be with Zach all afternoon.

617
00:49:17,916 --> 00:49:21,086
- I'll see you two for lunch at the hospital.
